Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
Strategically located in the emerging urban center of South Orange County, 120 Vantis offers Class A office space with structured parking and efficient floor plates that work well for single or multi-tenant users. Lobby and interior finishes, construction and materials are all of the highest standards.
A Vantis address also puts tenants within walking distance of a wide array of shops, restaurants and entertainment at Aliso Viejo Town Center and rewards them with a host of leisure-time amenities, including scenic walking trails and inviting parks. In addition, nearby freeways make it easy to reach other recreation destinations throughout South Orange County, and the beaches of Dana Point and Laguna are just minutes away.
